metadata.name: RoverX Early Access Pass #1
metadata.description:
RoverX ([https://roverx.io](https://roverx.io/)) lets you carry NFTs in your pocket. Serious NFT traders use RoverX Android and iOS apps to track their NFT portfolio and receive alerts for floor price changes, new offers, listing expired, offer accepted, etc.

The RoverX early access pass gives you FREE access to Roverx android and iOS apps.

It also gives you access to RoverX web-app where you can use our Advanced filters to find undervalued collections.
